{
  "texts": [
    "The goal is to ascertain that technology-empowered learning support genuinely enhances students' learning process in a consistent and unbiased manner.",
    "Given ChatGPT's complex nature of generating varied responses based on myriad prompts, the call for enhancing methodological rigor through future validation studies becomes both timely and essential.",
    "For example, in-depth prompt validation and blind feedback assessment studies could be employed to meticulously probe the consistency and quality of ChatGPT's responses.",
    "Also, comparative analysis with different AI models can be useful.",
    "From an educational standpoint, our research findings advocate for the integration of ChatGPT as a feedback resource with peer feedback within higher education environments for essay writing tasks since there is a complementary role potential for pee-generated and ChatGPT-generated feedback."
  ]
}